{"tid":2039175,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本政府擬擴大限制使用華為產品","createTime":"2020-05-28T01:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T03:12:50.000Z","uid":64191,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2feb630fe4b2d1823ca3d2409eb004a0c0fe09b1","tid":2039175,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T01:27:03.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】日本《讀賣新聞》報道，日本政府將修改針對採購通訊設備規定方針，擴大禁止使用包括華為及中興通訊等中國電訊設備商的產品。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，日本政府於去年四月開始，已針對政府部門採購電訊設備制定方針，要求在採購時不但要考慮價格，還要考慮安全保障風險；此舉是為了排除使用中國大型電訊設備商，包括華為和中興通訊的產品。<br />\n<br />\n而日本政府近日計劃跟隨美國，加強防範國民個人資料被竊取及遭黑客攻擊，將會修改採購方針，將禁止使用中國電訊商品範圍進一步擴大至與官方有關的96個法人團體，包括原子能研究開發機構、年金機構及營運個人身分相關系統的地方公共團體資訊系統等。<br />\n<br />\n新修訂方針將於六月推出，法人團體在採購電訊設備前，需與內閣網路資訊安全中心商討；如果發現有安全風險，中心會要求更換。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=392479\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392479&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PhUAsmJrpgm%2FsQZzOZZuI0I%3D&h=74effc06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392479&h=ebcbb7b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=392479</a>"},{"pid":"c23bc3a5928d67562f1fbc333852560b78e50fc7","tid":2039175,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T01:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a920c20e600a50edc5aaf91e4d98645dcfd95a7b","tid":2039175,"uid":99962,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T01:28:13.000Z","msg":"日本通街都係華為手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9fb1a1fe838899c14754016805fd346575cc42","tid":2039175,"uid":244332,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T01:30:29.000Z","msg":"歸隊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\